Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're not the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:14.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...my home town and this dirty city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:15.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a city that a child like you should see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roanapur at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:23.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:28.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must believe in your people from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do. I believe in them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:33.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that they'll come and save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:36.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can feel it in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:45.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That the maid who you believe in will come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:49.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it'll come true or not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:54.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you must have a great family if you have such strong faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:01.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I always wonder how my family feels about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you miss your mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:12.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I did, I would have said goodbye to this place long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, that's a pointless story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:21.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the story of a brat who chases after mama when it's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:23.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're just talking about ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:26.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To see if you hold in your heart something to believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:33.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, if I'm ever kidnapped, are you going to wave your Cutlass around and come save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone stupid enough to get kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:45.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In this world you just bite off your navel, beg forgiveness for causing trouble to your comrades, and then die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See? These are my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but they're worth sticking with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:05.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just wish that maid of yours is as strong as you believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This hasn't seen much use lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This Cutlass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just kiddin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no point in wishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not when I'm stuck with a maid-obsessed brat from the fucking countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:23.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Be rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's making me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid I will not be able to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:37.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And he just reopened this bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:03.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She sure has something flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:09.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:12.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back! Kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please do as you must,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:21.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:07:02.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:14.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Kevlar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You better pay for all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:25.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've walked into a very bad fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:29.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that they're going at it is in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about we take off while they're busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take off? To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can go fishing at the Phuket beach until this cools down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in the mood for drinking with a gunfight on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}Giuliano Gemma is a famous actor in spaghetti westerns
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no Giuliano Gemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:47.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, will you hurry up and decide if I need to shoot or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:49.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave the kid here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:54.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go for a walk carrying a claymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But he's worth something, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The exit became a war zone while we were talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this kid isn't money anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:13.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:13.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:17.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, damn, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:19.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move from this spot until the gunfire dies down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:29.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When it gets quiet, go home to Venezuela with your maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I... didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that Roberta was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:44.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's not someone who would kill, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:53.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:02.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,10,000 dollars for the bottles, 15,000 dollars for the furniture,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,plus 20,000 dollars for the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now the problem is figuring out who to send the bill to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:10.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, is this your doing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do your friends need to tear up my shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:22.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're not my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who they are, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get quiet, you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lagoon Company! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to delivering our package?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jump to conclusions, Gregor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:51.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the package here? Did you ignore our contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I said don't jump to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk about the payment later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:08.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you were here, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The master has been very worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be helped if you are afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:23.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will explain myself later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:31.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Their eyes met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:35.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:41.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back, maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:46.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here would rather be alive than dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:50.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid. Stop it or we'll be the villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:55.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't start shooting, you'll get the young master home in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:58.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have to see his brains on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:10:59.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:06.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ignore us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have finished thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Una bendicion por los vivos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}A blessing for the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:54.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Una rama de flor por los muertos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:54.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}A flower branch for the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mercy for the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of flowers for the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.23,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Con una espada por la justicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.23,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}With a sword of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wield a sword for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:03.53,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Un castigo de muerte para los malvados.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:03.53,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}A punishment of death for the wicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:06.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The punishment of death for evildoers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:09.63,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Asi llegamos en el altar de los santos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:09.62,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Like this we arrive at the alter of the saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, we are not joining the line of saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Loveless family creed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:22.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will have the young master home in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:24.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, I must work by this creed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:27.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of Santa Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:29.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A hammer blow to all injustice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That... That bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:47.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:48.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:57.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go and Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:04.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hunting dog of Florencia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:04.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}Florencia is a municipality in the Caquetá Department, Colombia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a crazy bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This makes the Battle of Khe Sanh look like a picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}Khe Sanh was a particularly bloody battle in the Vietnam war
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is Revy all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The wound doesn't seem serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But she's got a concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:19.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:31.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:32.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:35.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fucking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:43.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:47.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:49.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:53.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:14.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:20.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember, from what you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:28.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,El perro de cassa de Florencia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:28.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}The hunting dog of Florence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The hunting dog from Florencia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:34.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:37.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even Jesus couldn't have guessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:40.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These four years since you left the Colombian Revolutionary Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:45.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,everyone from the drug cartels to Interpol has been after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:50.09,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The cartels put a 40,000 dollar bounty on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:52.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:01.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Finally luck is on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:06.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I bring your head back, I'll be a lieutenant of the cartel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have a reason to keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you will excuse me, I must be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:20.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:22.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's unbelievably thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:45.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to leave the kid behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't leave him in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:56.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:57.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can't hear anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like her footsteps are getting closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and her black maid's outfit is about to appear from that fiery exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up and get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a place we can run to on this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a killer robot from the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing different from the movies is that Schwarzenegger isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny and I can't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've got her precious young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just head for the port! Hurry to the Lagoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:07.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news doesn't take much effort to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Her code name is "Bloodhound".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:17.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She got it because once locked onto her prey, she always kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:22.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're calling, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's really coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:41.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wake Revy up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time for her to be comfortably sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:43.76,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:44.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:56.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Benisov, what is the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Yellow Flag has been mostly destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Bloodhound and Lagoon are both gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:20.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But a Primus was seen heading towards the city on the main street ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:24.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do not leave that spot, Sergeant. Continue gathering information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:25.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:26.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What shall I tell the shop's owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him not to worry about insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:32.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am heading towards the city with a squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:39.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Capitan, are you going to war after so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:43.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Playing mafia is not good, it dulls your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:44.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no reason not to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We owe Lagoon...no, we owe Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go, comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cock your hammers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head to the port using these back-roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're out to sea, no matter who she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No good, Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lose speed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Her radiator was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:06.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She can't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:13.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should have paid more attention to Rock's joke, Benny-Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:16.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine her as an invincible killer robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:17.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna punch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, get Revy up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:24.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When things get tight, we're going to need her gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! Revy! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:27.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benny, take the next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the main road and go at full speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:31.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:55.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:05.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It won't start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:19.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Benny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:34.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:44.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:20.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the top three most fearsome women in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:22.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This feels like Ground Zero.
